<h3><u>FAQ</u></h3>
  <p> This is the FAQ that is in the server. You can also find it <a href="https://discord.com/channels/699077627339735232/747858762857185320/747870753306968285">here</a>.</p>
  <p> <u>(Q)  How can I level up and check my level?</u> <br>
A member levels up in the server by talking and chatting, The level-up notice will appear in whatever channel you are talking in when you level up. Do arank in #bot-commands to check your current rank/level.
<br> <br>
 <u>(Q) How do I check/appeal warnings?</u><br>
A member can search there current warnings in the server by doing >search in #bot-commands. To appeal warning you must dm @ModMail#5460.
<br> <br>
 <u>(Q) If someone is breaking rules what do I do?</u><br>
If a member is breaking rules and you see them, a staff member will take care of the situation, if needed feel free to ping staff!
<br> <br>
<u>(Q) Can I get a role?</u><br>
If you are begging for staff roles you will be warned, for roles like the youtuber, gifter,and other roles you may dm @ModMail#5460 to see how you can obtain them. Check #roles-information for more info.
<br> <br>
<u> (Q) How can I partner?</u><br>
To partner with this server, you must read #partner-requirements first, if you meet these requirements please dm a partnership manager or an admin and they will assist you!
<br> <br>
 <u>(Q) Can we swear in the chat?</u><br>
Yes, you can swear in chat. You may not direct swear words to people, if you do so you will be warned. No racial slurs are allowed, if used it is an automatic ban.
<br> <br>
 <u>(Q) How can I host a giveaway?</u><br>
For hosting a giveaway you must contact an admin. It depends on the prize if we are willing to do a requirement for the giveaway.
<br> <br>
<u>(Q) Do you guys have staff applications?</u><br>
We do have staff applications, however, staff applications will be announced in #announcements when they open/close.
<br> <br>
<u>(Q) Are we allowed to speak any language here?</u><br>
This is an English speaking server only, if you speak any other language you will be given a verbal warning followed by another warning.
<br> <br>
<u>(Q) How can I post in #self-advertising?</u><br>
To post in #self-advertising all you need to do is get level 5, do arank in #bot-commands to see your level. </p>
<br> <br>
<p class="bottomNote"> This website was made by @WheezyBread63 #0001 <br> This is the official website of <a href="https://discord.gg/FzTDVDd"> Echo Circle </a>

